content.rendered:
Directed by C. Prem Kumar.

Written by C. Prem Kumar.

Cast Vijay Sethupathi(Ramachandran ‘Ram’ Krishnamoorthy). Adithya Bhaskar(Young Ramachandran ‘Ram’ Krishnamoorthy). Trisha Krishnan(Janaki ‘Janu’ Devi Sugumar). Gouri Kishan(Young Janaki ‘Janu’ Devi Sugumar). Devadarshini Chetan(Subhashini ‘Subha’). Niyathi Kadambi(Young Subhashini ‘Subha’). Janakaraj(‘Kaval Deivam’, the school watchman (as Janagaraj)). Bagavathi Perumal(Murali). Surya(Young Murali). Rajkumar(Surya). Murugadass(Sathiesh (as Aadukalam Murugadoss)). Gowthamraj(Young Sathish). Varsha Bollamma(Prabha). Kavithalaya Krishnan(Kalai Selvan, barber). Shyam Prasad(Hotel Receptionist)

Language Tamil.

Producers Nandagopal. S. Nanthagopal.

Production Goldmines Telefilms. Madras Enterprises.
